---
title: Hot Chicken Breast Sandwiches with Peas, Gravy and Creamy Mash
description: This comfort dish is inspired by the Quebecois 'Hot Chicken Sandwich'. In our version, we drop the 'sandwich' and make an open-faced wonder! Rich chicken gravy smothers tender chicken atop toasted buns, with pops of bright flavour from the green peas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hot-chicken-breast-sandwiches-54c864af.jpg
